site_name: Colindale Gardens (former Peel Centre), Phase 2 (Blocks ABCD)
description: Resubmission for the approval of Reserved Matters relating to Phases 2D, 2E, 2F and 2G of Development Stage 2 of the Colindale Gardens development (former Peel Centre); seeking approval for details relating to Layout, Scale, Appearance and Landscaping. Submission is pursuant to outline planning permission reference H/04753/14 dated 23/12/2015 as amended by S73 Application 16/7836/S73 dated 05/05/17, involving the erection of 1,220 units in the form of 82 x studio, 343 x 1 bedroom, 658 x 2 bedroom, 137 x 3 bedroom units together with the provision of 6,255 sqm of non-residential floorspace containing a mix of A1, A2, A3, A4, C3, D1 (including new Health Centre and Nursery) and D2 uses
